  Scenario: Successfully filter products by boolean value for boolean attributes and refresh the grid
    Given the following products:
      | sku   | family  | handmade |
      | pants | tshirts | 1        |
      | shirt | tshirts | 0        |
      | shoes | tshirts | 0        |
